OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny spells and showers,
OL,6,Fthough many places staying. Heaviest
OL,7,Fof the showers across the north with
OL,8,Fisolated hail and thunder with gusty
OL,9,Fwinds. Cloud and rain spread from the
OL,10,Fsouthwest later. Remaining warm in the
OL,11,Fsoutheast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FEarly showers fade, leaving
OL,14,Fclear spells. Cloud and rain spread in
OL,15,Ffrom the west turning heavy and gusty
OL,16,Fin the north. Staying mild, with
OL,17,Fisolated mist in the southeast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
