OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FMist clears the southeast to a
OL,6,Flargely dry start with early sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Rain moves eastwards across
OL,8,Fthe country through the day. Heavy
OL,9,Fshowers follow in the northwest. Winds
OL,10,Fstrengthening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
